SECURITY
Run mapene-mcp on a private network only. Set MCP_AUTH_TOKEN to require
`Authorization: Bearer <token>` on all routes except /health (the server is
fail-closed when the token is unset). Configure MCP_ALLOWED_ORIGIN for CORS.

